_sText:
My first surf map! It is not really hard, I would say its about easy to medium!

I've added trigger_multiple zones on stages and end zone(Look below) I'm also listing the info_teleports after on each stage after the trigger_multiple name for the sake of ease with servers running certain timer mods.

- Level 1: "stage1" ~ 1.1
- Level 2: "stage2" ~ 2.2
- Level 3: "stage3" ~ 3.3
- Level 4: "stage4" ~ 4.4
- Level 5: "stage5" ~ 5.5
- Level 6: "stage6" ~ 6.6
- Level 7: "stage7" ~ 7.7
- Level 8: "stage8" ~ 8.8
- Level 9: "stage9" ~ 9.9
- Level 10: "stage10" ~ 10.10
- Level 11: "stage11" ~ 11.11
- Level 12: "stage12" ~ 12.12
- End zone: "endzone"

Another thing, you can telehop the entire map if yo nofail every stage, if you fail on a stage after you've entered it for the first time that run you'll be prevented from telehopping it again unless you restart the map.
